output.analysis:
Let's analyze this post according to our criteria:
1. Has CMF: Yes, contains "CMF 11240017" 2. Refers to candidate: Yes, explicitly mentions Marcel Ciolacu, a presidential candidate 3. Addresses wide population: Yes, it's a paid Facebook/Instagram ad with 15,000-19,999 impressions 4. Electoral objective: Yes, explicitly calls for votes ("Votați Marcel Ciolacu, președinte!") 5. Journalism: No, this is clearly campaign material, not journalistic content 6. Personal opinion: No, this is an organized campaign message with CMF number
The post is particularly problematic because: - It explicitly calls for voting for Marcel Ciolacu as president - It's still running after the campaign period for presidential elections ended - It has significant reach (15,000+ impressions) - It's clearly electoral propaganda with a CMF number - It's paid advertising, not organic content

conclusion.electoral-propaganda-analysis: This is clearly electoral propaganda because: - Contains explicit call to vote ("Votați Marcel Ciolacu, președinte!") - Has CMF number (11240017) - Is paid advertising - Targets wide audience (15,000+ impressions) - Promotes presidential candidate after campaign period ended
conclusion.message-for-police: Infomed Pro SRL, pentru incalcarea articolului 55 t) din Legea 370/2004, prin continuarea propagandei electorale după încheierea campaniei prezidențiale, promovând candidatul ION-MARCEL CIOLACU pentru funcția de președinte prin intermediul unei reclame plătite pe Facebook (ID: 1126375062244385) cu mesajul explicit "Votați Marcel Ciolacu, președinte!". Materialul promotional, marcat cu CMF 11240017, a avut un impact semnificativ, atingând între 15.000 și 19.999 de persoane după ora 18:00 pe 23.11.2024, încălcând astfel perioada legală de campanie electorală pentru alegerile prezidențiale.
